<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>UEC Campus Explorer and Uploader</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>UEC Campus Explorer and Uploader</h1>
  <br>
  <p>授業を検索したり、授業の感想を共有できたりします</p>
  <h2>授業一覧</h2>
  <% (2019..2019).each do |year| %>
    <h3><%= link_to("#{year}年度", "/#{year}") %></h3>
  <% end %>
  <br>
  <h3>最近のコメント</h3>
  <% @comments[0..-2].each do |comment| # ラストはnewでできた空レコードなので %>
    <div class="media text-muted pt-3">
      <p class="media-body pb-3 mb-0 lh-125 border-bottom border-gray">
      <strong class="d-block text-gray-dark">@<%= comment.contributor  || '匿名さん' %></strong>
      <%= comment.created_at.strftime('%Y/%m/%d %H:%M') %>
      <%= comment.course.course_title_japanese %><br>
      <%= comment.text %>
      </p>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</body>
</html>
